    "summary": "ARLINGTON, Va., July 14, 2026--Homes.com, a CoStar Group (NASDAQ: CSGP) leading online residential marketplace, released its June 2026 housing market report showing that the national median sale price rose to $401,000, up 1.5% from a year earlier. Home sales increased 6.1% year over year, while active listings were 4.2% higher than a year ago, indicating that both demand and supply continued to expand at a measured pace.",
